data.description: This 3,020 sqft home sits beautifully on an extra-large corner lot. Featured with 4 beds, 2.5 baths, 2 car garage, high ceilings in the living room with a wood-burning fireplace and butler's pantry. A formal dining area is located at the front of the home adorned with beautiful tile. This room could also be used in many other ways! New carpet flooring throughout this 2-story home. Gorgeous Remodeled Island Kitchen with a farmhouse sink, Beautiful Quartz countertops with its own study/craft area and beautiful windows.    Newport is a master planned community located just 30 minutes from Downtown Houston. Such amenities as the community pool, tennis courts, gym, private lake and river access, parks, walking trails, splash pad, Stonebridge 18-hole golf course, pro shop and country club making Newport a wonderful place to call home.
